106  virtual bool match(UCharIterator lemma_begin, UCharIterator lemma_end, const compressed_delaf::entry &e) const
107  {
108  typename ptr_list<compressed_delaf_entry_filter<UCharIterator> >::const_iterator i(compressed_delaf_entry_filters.begin());
109  for (; i != compressed_delaf_entry_filters.end(); ++i)
110  if ((*i)->match(lemma_begin, lemma_end, e))
111  return true;
112  return false;
113  }
114 
115  virtual bool same_type_less(const compressed_delaf_entry_filter<UCharIterator> &l) const
116  { return *this < dynamic_cast<const union_compressed_delaf_entry_filter &>(l); }
117 
118  virtual std::ostream& serialize(std::ostream& out) const
119  {
120  if (compressed_delaf_entry_filters.empty())
121  return out;
122  typename ptr_list<compressed_delaf_entry_filter<UCharIterator> >::const_iterator i(compressed_delaf_entry_filters.begin());
123  (*i)->serialize(out);
124  ++i;
125  for (; i != compressed_delaf_entry_filters.end(); ++i)
126  {
127  out << '+';
128  (*i)->serialize(out);
129  }
130  return out;
131  }
132 
133  virtual std::wostream& wserialize(std::wostream& out) const
134  {
135  if (compressed_delaf_entry_filters.empty())
136  return out;
137  typename ptr_list<compressed_delaf_entry_filter<UCharIterator> >::const_iterator i(compressed_delaf_entry_filters.begin());
138  (*i)->wserialize(out);
139  ++i;
140  for (; i != compressed_delaf_entry_filters.end(); ++i)
141  {
142  out << L'+';
143  (*i)->wserialize(out);
144  }
145  return out;
146  }
147 
148  virtual void u_write(FILE *f) const
149  {
150  if (compressed_delaf_entry_filters.empty())
151  return;
152  typename ptr_list<compressed_delaf_entry_filter<UCharIterator> >::const_iterator i(compressed_delaf_entry_filters.begin());
153  (*i)->u_write(f);
154  ++i;
155  for (; i != compressed_delaf_entry_filters.end(); ++i)
156  {
157  u_fputc('+', f);
158  (*i)->u_write(f);
159  }
160  }
161  };
